21/06/2019: Comienzo a familiarizarme con el tema, leyendo e instalando los programas que seràn utilizados en la predicción de péptidos:

Programa	Leido	Instalado	Desc.				Paper
AntiBP2		O	X		Red neural entrenada		AntiBP2: Improved version of antibacterial peptide prediction 
APD3 		O	X		Base de datos			APD3: the antimicrobial peptide database as a tool for research and education
iAMP-2L		O	X		Predictor que no entiendo	iAMP-2L: A two-level multi-label classifier for identifying antimicrobial peptides and their functional types
DBAASP v2	O	X		Base de datos			DBAASP v.2: an enhanced database of structure and antimicrobial/cytotoxic activity of natural and synthetic peptides
AMPA		O	X		Predictor que no comprendo	AMPA: an automated web server for prediction of protein antimicrobial regions
AmPEP		O	X		Serie de predictor		AmPEP: Sequence-based prediction of antimicrobial peptides using distribution patterns of amino acid properties and random forest			
iAMPpred	O	X		Predictores			Predicting antimicrobial peptides with improved accuracy by incorporating the compositional, physico-chemical and structural features into Chou’s general PseAAC
CAMPR3		O	X		Composición AA			CAMP R3 : a database on sequences, structures and signatures of antimicrobial peptides
modlAMP		O	*		paquete 			modlAMP: Python for antimicrobial peptides

No todos son instalables. Servidores web:
1) AntiBP2: https://webs.iiitd.edu.in/raghava/antibp2/submit.html
2) APD3: http://aps.unmc.edu/AP/main.php
3) iAMP-2L: http://www.jci-bioinfo.cn/iAMP-2L
4) DBAASP v2: https://dbaasp.org/
5) Ampa: http://tcoffee.crg.cat/apps/ampa/do
6) iAMPpred: http://cabgrid.res.in:8080/amppred/server.php

Notas:
AntiBP2 - Es peor a su predecesor segun: "Empirical comparison of web-based antimicrobial peptide prediction tools" - y el  anterior tambièn puede venir con lios 
APD3 - Puedo subir un pèptido a la vez, aún no sé como funciona.
iAMP-2L - El infierno se va a llenar de chocolate antes de que entienda como funciona. Solo puedo subir de a 500 a la vez via web
DBAASP v2 - Tiene la opciòn de predecir péptidos mediante el uso de descriptores de las propiedades físicas de los péptidos. Pero se especializa en unùnico tipo de categoría de pep. anti microbiano  (cationic linier peptides)
iAMPpred - Basado en features, candidato para todos
modlAMP - Packete de python con cosas varias. Sería ideal para Herman

This analysis allows us to confirm that the best-performing AMP predictor is CAMPR3(RF), followed by CAMPR3(SVM) and then ADAM.

ALERTA: We see, for example, that CAMPR3(SVM) is largely indifferent to sequence length until the query is 100 amino acids long, at which point the sequences are all assigned scores very close to 1.0. CAMPR3(RF) shows a similar, though not quite as pronounced, trend. Some of the other predictors, including ADAM, MLAMP and BAGEL3, show length dependencies.


