	-> "Alternatively, the β-conglycinin amino acid sequence, the main source of the bioactive peptides from fractions F1 and F2, was used to screen potential antimicrobial sequences using the AMPA algorithm available at http://tcoffee.crg.cat/apps/ampa/do (Torrent et al., 2011)."

